  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK425">
<l>ulakan taḻīiya toṭpa malartaluṅ</l>
<l>kūmpalu milla taṟivu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>To secure the friendship of the great is true wisdom; it is (also) wisdom to keep (that friendship unchanged, and) not opening and closing (like the lotus flower).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
